622
01:18:25,320 --> 01:18:27,914
And I have character.

623
01:18:28,080 --> 01:18:32,153
Form a line across the room!

624
01:18:32,320 --> 01:18:35,118
Fill this gap!

625
01:18:35,280 --> 01:18:39,353
