637
01:19:28,560 --> 01:19:35,796
Who does this disgusting ribbon
belong to?

638
01:19:37,920 --> 01:19:43,472
I shall personally see to it
that the demented Lilliputian -

639
01:19:43,640 --> 01:19:48,998
