678
01:26:04,280 --> 01:26:08,114
- I have the adoption papers.
- What?

679
01:26:08,280 --> 01:26:12,796
- Where did you get those?
- From a book in the library.

680
01:26:12,960 --> 01:26:16,236
Are you hearing this, Harry?

681
01:26:16,400 --> 01:26:20,473
- You just have to sign.
- I'll be an only child again!

682
01:26:20,640 --> 01:26:23,438
I can't think with all these sirens!

683
01:26:25,040 --> 01:26:27,838
What do you think, pumpkin?

684
01:26:29,400 --> 01:26:36,272
You're the only daughter I ever had.
And I never understood you.

685
01:26:38,920 --> 01:26:42,390
Who's got a pen?

686
01:26:42,560 --> 01:26:46,348
- Here.
- Thanks.

687
01:26:47,400 --> 01:26:54,829
<i>This was perhaps the first decent</i>
<i>thing they ever did for Matilda.</i>

688
01:26:55,000 --> 01:26:58,470
And here.

689
01:27:00,640 --> 01:27:04,428
Come here. Turn around.

690
01:27:06,320 --> 01:27:12,509
- You won't want support payments?
- No. We have everything we need.

691
01:27:12,680 --> 01:27:16,195
Let's roll.

692
01:27:29,280 --> 01:27:33,353
<i>So Harry and Zinnia got away.</i>
<i>And as bad as things were, -</i>

693
01:27:33,520 --> 01:27:37,479
<i>- that's how good they became.</i>

694
01:27:39,200 --> 01:27:45,514
<i>Miss Honey was made</i>
<i>principal of the school.</i>

695
01:27:45,680 --> 01:27:51,198
<i>And Matilda found, to her surprise,</i>
<i>that life could be fun.</i>

696
01:27:51,360 --> 01:27:54,830
<i>She decided to have</i>
<i>as much fun as possible.</i>

697
01:27:55,000 --> 01:27:58,675
<i>After all, she was a very smart kid.</i>

698
01:28:12,640 --> 01:28:19,478
<i>Matilda and Miss Honey each got</i>
<i>what they had always wanted:</i>

699
01:28:19,640 --> 01:28:23,315
<i>A loving family.</i>

700
01:28:23,480 --> 01:28:28,076
<i>And Matilda never had to use</i>
<i>her powers again.</i>

701
01:28:28,240 --> 01:28:31,516
<i>Well. I mean almost never.</i>

702
01:28:40,520 --> 01:28:43,080
"Call me Ishmael."

703
01:28:43,240 --> 01:28:49,120
"Some years ago,
never mind how long, precisely..."

704
01:33:55,680 --> 01:34:00,276
English subtitles - IFT

